Today, we reached a sobering milestone: 300,000 dead from the COVID-19 pandemic. It is beyond time for President Trump to commit to a peaceful, comprehensive transition of power so that President Biden and VP Harris are ready on day one to beat the coronavirus and save lives.

The American people have spoken, and now the Electoral College has reiterated: Joe Biden is the next President of the United States, and Kamala Harris is our Vice President-elect. Their leadership cannot come soon enough.
